<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - RaketMo</title>
    <!-- Tailwind CSS CDN -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-800 p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white shadow-lg rounded-xl p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-10 lg:p-12 border border-gray-200">
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-6 sm:mb-8">Privacy Policy for RaketMo</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 text-center mb-8">Effective Date: July 24, 2025</p>

        <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            RaketMo, Inc. ("RaketMo," "we," "our," or "us") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy describes how we
            collect, use, store, and protect your personal information when you use our platform, services, website, and
            mobile application (collectively, the "Platform"). By using the Platform, you agree to the collection and use
            of your information in accordance with this Privacy Policy.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">We collect the following types of personal and non-personal information:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li><strong class="font-medium">Account Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, password, and payment details</li>
            <li><strong class="font-medium">Profile Information:</strong> Photos, descriptions, reviews, task history, and availability</li>
            <li><strong class="font-medium">Location Data:</strong> Provided by your device with your consent</li>
            <li><strong class="font-medium">Usage Information:</strong> Pages viewed, features used, referral URLs, app interactions</li>
            <li><strong class="font-medium">Device and Technical Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, operating system, mobile device ID</li>
            <li><strong class="font-medium">Background Check Data (Optional):</strong> If you choose to undergo a background check, our third-party provider (Checkr) may collect criminal history and identity verification information</li>
            <li><strong class="font-medium">Licensing and Certification Data (If Applicable):</strong> Documents submitted voluntarily to verify qualifications</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">We use your information to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li>Operate, maintain, and improve the Platform</li>
            <li>Facilitate communication between Clients and Taskers</li>
            <li>Process payments securely</li>
            <li>Perform identity verification (where applicable)</li>
            <li>Conduct optional background checks via Checkr (if selected)</li>
            <li>Analyze trends, usage, and user behavior</li>
            <li>Send account updates, security alerts, and promotional materials</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. Sharing Your Information</h2>
        <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">We do not sell your personal information. We may share your data with:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li><strong class="font-medium">Other Users:</strong> Basic profile data shared with Clients or Taskers as part of the service</li>
            <li><strong class="font-medium">Service Providers:</strong> Including Stripe (payments) and Checkr (background checks)</li>
            <li><strong class="font-medium">Legal Authorities:</strong> If required to comply with applicable law or law enforcement requests</li>
            <li><strong class="font-medium">Business Transfers:</strong> In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. Background Checks and Licensing (Optional)</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li>Taskers may choose to undergo a background check using Checkr. This is entirely optional and not required to use the Platform.</li>
            <li>If submitted, license or certification documents are stored and displayed to users at the Tasker's discretion.</li>
            <li>RaketMo is not responsible for the accuracy, completeness, or current status of background check results or licensing documentation.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">5. Your Choices and Rights</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li>You may access and update your account information at any time</li>
            <li>You may opt out of promotional emails by following the unsubscribe link</li>
            <li>You may request deletion of your account and personal data, subject to legal and operational requirements</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">6. Data Security</h2>
        <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            We use reasonable administrative, physical, and technical safeguards to protect your data. However, no
            system is 100% secure.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">7. Data Retention</h2>
        <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            We retain user data as long as your account is active or as needed to provide services and comply with our
            legal obligations.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">8. Children’s Privacy</h2>
        <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            RaketMo is not intended for children under the age of 18. We do not knowingly collect personal data from
            children.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">9. California Privacy Rights (CCPA)</h2>
        <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">If you are a California resident, you may have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li>Request access to and deletion of your personal information</li>
            <li>Know what personal data we collect and disclose</li>
            <li>Opt out of the sale (we do not sell personal data)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">To exercise your rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:support@raketmo.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">support@raketmo.com</a>.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">10. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p class="mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            We may update this Privacy Policy at any time. We will notify you of material changes through email or a
            prominent notice on the Platform.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">11. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed">If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, contact us at:</p>
        <address class="not-italic mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            <p>RaketMo, Inc.</p>
            <p><a href="mailto:support@raketmo.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">support@raketmo.com</a></p>
            <p><a href="https://www.raketmo.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">www.raketmo.com</a></p>
        </address>

        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 text-center mt-8 pt-4 border-t border-gray-200">
            Copyright &copy; 2025 RaketMo, Inc. All rights reserved.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>